Package: specvec
Title: Abundance-Aware Species and Community Embeddings
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gilles", "Colling", , "gilles.colling051@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3070-6066"))
Description: Learns species and community embeddings from ecological
    co-occurrence data with abundance-aware weighting. Turns a long
    'plot x species (x abundance)' table into species vectors and
    first-class community vectors, and ships a benchmark harness that
    scores embedding methods (correspondence analysis, pointwise mutual
    information, abundance-weighted PMI, and GloVe) on neutral ecological
    tasks. A method is a registered '(weighting, factorization)' pair, so
    new methods are added by registration rather than by copying code.
